# Laravel Extra Architecture

## Actions

- Place business logic in `app/Actions`.
- Give each action a single public `handle()` method.
- Keep actions reusable from HTTP, console, jobs, queues, and tests.

## DTOs

- Place DTOs in `app/Dto`.
- Prefer readonly DTOs.
- Pass DTOs into actions instead of large untyped arrays.

## Controllers

- Keep controllers small.
- Validate input with Form Requests.
- Delegate business logic to actions.
